              li Vim
              li Emacs
              li WebStorm
              li Atom
              li Eclipse
              li And many more...
          section
            h2 Tslint
            p An extensible linter for the TypeScript language.
            p: small: a(href='https://github.com/palantir/tslint') github.com/palantir/tslint
        section
          section
            h1 Getting started
          section
            pre: code.js.
              // Install
              npm install -g typescript

              // Compile
              tsc helloworld.ts
          section
            h2 Tutorials
